{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b88960faec","title":"毛泽东关于注意发表国外对华评论问题的批语","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"abb4ed3ef8","index":0,"year":1959,"month":9,"day":4,"articleId":"b88960faec"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9102e3d902","type":"title","text":"毛泽东关于注意发表国外对华评论问题的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b88960faec"},{"id":"c86ad1c4fe","type":"appellation","text":"乔木、冷西：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b88960faec"},{"id":"1e6c2d2bad","type":"paragraph","text":"(一)此件也似可发表；(二)日本及西方的一些有利评论，宜大量发表，污蔑评论，也要发表，加以驳斥。反华越恶毒，对我们越有利，因为敌人处在被动地位，不得翻身了。以上请酌。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b88960faec"},{"id":"40d428660a","type":"paragraph","text":"再者：过一会，例如在国庆节后半个月的时候，将赫鲁晓夫反公社的演说，在人民日报发表，使他越处于被动，使全国人民知道赫鲁晓夫是反公社的。是否可行，请先想一下，届时中央再做决定。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b88960faec"},{"id":"2433743acb","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东九月四日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b88960faec"}],"page":{"id":"95090fd27d","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"b88960faec","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}